Class MultiParameterizedNavigationCommand

java.lang.Object
gw.api.quickjump.QuickjumpCommand
gw.api.quickjump.ProgressivelyDisclosedCommand
gw.api.quickjump.MultiParameterizedNavigationCommand
public abstract class MultiParameterizedNavigationCommand extends ProgressivelyDisclosedCommand
QuickJump command which takes the user to some page expecting multiple arguments, which are entered by the user.

      protected abstract String[] getCommandDisplaySuffixes()
      Description copied from class: ProgressivelyDisclosedCommand
      Returns the parameters hint to display as an array of Strings. These strings are displayed after the command name in the autocomplete suggestions for this command to indicate to the user what each parameter means.
      Overrides:
      getCommandDisplaySuffixes in class ProgressivelyDisclosedCommand

    • getCommandDisplaySuffix

      protected final String getCommandDisplaySuffix()
      Description copied from class: ProgressivelyDisclosedCommand
      Returns the parameter hint to display after the command name, before parameter entry has started. This string is displayed after the command name in the autocomplete suggestion for this command before the user has entered a command, in order to indicate to the user what parameters they will have to enter.
      Specified by:
      getCommandDisplaySuffix in class ProgressivelyDisclosedCommand
